TEXT 912 1816 Left 2 ;FILE 1: LTC1871_Startup_NoCSS.asc â BASELINE STARTUP CHARACTERISATION
TEXT 912 1840 Left 2 ;PURPOSE: Confirm and precisely quantify startup overshoot with no CSS cap (current hardware state)
TEXT 912 1864 Left 2 ;CONFIG: VIN=9.6V fixed | Iload=2A DC (worst-case: full load at startup) | No soft-start cap on RUN pin
TEXT 912 1888 Left 2 ;.tran 0 5m 0 captures FULL startup from t=0 (no Tstart skip â startup IS the subject)
TEXT 912 1912 Left 2 ;KEY METRICS: Vout_peak [V] | overshoot [%] | t_peak [s] | t_settle [s] | Vout_SS [V]
TEXT 912 1936 Left 2 ;HARDWARE RISK: CM4 absolute max ~15V | Overshoot limit: <13.2V (<10%) for safe bring-up
